OL,3,CIs Narendra Modi set for victory in
OL,4,CIndia's general election?
OL,6,FAhead of India's general election
OL,7,Fresult, ITV News' Asia Correspondent
OL,8,FDebi Edward reflects on why a Narendra
OL,9,FModi victory could be so divisive.
OL,11,FAt seven o'clock this morning we
OL,12,Farrived in one of the poorer
OL,13,Fcommunities in Delhi, where they are
OL,14,Frelying on water rations.
OL,16,FIt was already 32C when the water
OL,17,Ftanker arrived and there was a huge
OL,18,Fcommotion as men, women and children
OL,19,Frushed towards the pipes, which
OL,20,Fsuddenly sprouted from all sides of
OL,21,Fthe vehicle.
