OL,6,FThey frantically filled up buckets,
OL,7,Fbottles and whatever vessel they had,
OL,8,Fwith as much water as they could carry.
OL,10,FIt was a far cry from the orderly
OL,11,Fqueues we've seen of people lining up
OL,12,Fto vote over the past six weeks. The
OL,13,Fcapital is in the grip of a punishing
OL,14,Fheatwave, and a critical water
OL,15,Fshortage.
OL,17,FLarge parts of the country are
OL,18,Fenduring extreme temperatures for days
OL,19,Fon end. But was barely mentioned
OL,20,Fduring the entire 44-day, seven phase,
OL,21,Fvoting process.
