OL,3,CIs Narendra Modi set for victory in
OL,4,CIndia's general election?
OL,6,FOn the final weekend, while India
OL,7,FPrime Minister was enjoying his post-
OL,8,Felection meditation in a cool coastal
OL,9,Ftemple, more than 50 people -
OL,10,Fincluding 33 election workers - died
OL,11,Fdue to heatstroke.
OL,13,FAlthough the heat is thought to have
OL,14,Fcontributed to a lower turnout in some
OL,15,Fconstituencies, more than half a
OL,16,Fbillion people have still had their
OL,17,Fsay. That's just over half of the 970
OL,18,Fmillion registered voters.
