OL,3,CIs Narendra Modi set for victory in
OL,4,CIndia's general election?
OL,6,FExit polls suggest Mr Modi and his
OL,7,FHindu nationalist party, the Bharatiya
OL,8,FJanata Party (BJP), have secured a
OL,9,Fthird term.
OL,11,FThese polls have proved inaccurate in
OL,12,Fthe past, and on this occasion, there
OL,13,Fwere some which had certain parties
OL,14,Fwinning more seats than they had
OL,15,Fcontested.
OL,17,FHowever, if the predictions are even
OL,18,Fclose to correct, Mr Modi will owe his
OL,19,Fvictory to a slick campaign which has
OL,20,Fpresented him as the embodiment of
OL,21,FIndia.
