OL,3,CIs Narendra Modi set for victory in
OL,4,CIndia's general election?
OL,6,FHis rousing rally speeches were more
OL,7,Flike sermons, and his party has spent
OL,8,Fbillions on social media and an army
OL,9,Fof influencers to amplify his cult
OL,10,Fpersona.
OL,12,FWe watched Harish Burnwal broadcasting
OL,13,Fto his followers on YouTube. His
OL,14,Fchannel has almost a million
OL,15,Fsubscribers, and he was in no doubt Mr
OL,16,FModi has won another majority.
OL,18,FHe said messages flood in during his
OL,19,Flivestreams and they have been filled
OL,20,Fwith support for the prime minister.
