OL,3,CIs Narendra Modi set for victory in
OL,4,CIndia's general election?
OL,6,FMr Burnwal described Mr Modi as having
OL,7,Fan "aura", and said he has received
OL,8,Fcomments from around the world which
OL,9,Fshow the global Indian community is
OL,10,Falso backing him to win.
OL,12,FThat is not necessarily true for
OL,13,FMuslim Indians. Those we met at Monday
OL,14,Fprayer in Delhi were hoping the exit
OL,15,Fpolls are wrong.
OL,17,FDuring Mr Modi's first ten years in
OL,18,Fpower, Muslims have been subjected to
OL,19,Fviolence, and treated like second
OL,20,Fclass citizens.
