OL,3,CIs Narendra Modi set for victory in
OL,4,CIndia's general election?
OL,6,FIn election speeches the prime
OL,7,Fminister referred to Muslims as
OL,8,F"infiltrators" who have "many
OL,9,Fchildren". He even described a vote
OL,10,Ffor the opposition Congress party as
OL,11,F''vote jihad".
OL,13,FSuchrhetoric was no surprise for the
OL,14,Fauthor Ziya Us Salam, whose latest
OL,15,Fbook is called 'Being Muslim in Hindu
OL,16,FIndia'.
