OL,3,CIs Narendra Modi set for victory in
OL,4,CIndia's general election?
OL,6,FHe and his family have been subjected
OL,7,Fto abuse because of their faith, and
OL,8,Fhe says many Muslims have started
OL,9,Fchanging what they wear and how long
OL,10,Fthey keep their beards, in order not
OL,11,Fto stand out.
OL,13,FHe told me all minority faiths and
OL,14,Fcommunities could find life becoming
OL,15,Fharder during a third term of Mr Modi.
OL,17,FSuddenly in neighbourhoods where
OL,18,Fpeople of multiple faiths have lived
OL,19,Fin harmony, the seeds of discord are
OL,20,Fbeing sown.
