OL,3,CIs Narendra Modi set for victory in
OL,4,CIndia's general election?
OL,6,FHe feels they are in a fight to save
OL,7,Fthe Constitution of India and the
OL,8,Fsecular society it guarantees.
OL,10,FThis has been the longest and hottest
OL,11,Felection in India's history, and the
OL,12,Fresult could prove to be one of the
OL,13,Fmost divisive.
OL,15,FWe've heard many words used to
OL,16,Fdescribe Mr Modi. To some he is a
OL,17,Fdeity, to others a dictator. We will
OL,18,Fsoon know whether most Indians still
OL,19,Fwant to call him their prime minister.
